snippet.title: Share The Joy
snippet.description:
Hello My Friends, my name is Dean.
This channel I've created is all about videos that i think you will all enjoy.

If you're reading this then please support the new channel and Subscribe.
Leave a comment on a video and let me know what you think.
Hopefully if this account gets big then I will be doing giveaways in the future, so stick around and dont miss out..

Take care and have a great day.

#ShareTheJoy
